sentence: The war cry for justice was all over - Much to the chagrin of the authorities.
Khmer: សង្គ្រាមស្រែករកយុត្តិធម៌អស់ហើយ - ច្រើនក្នុងការចោទប្រកាន់របស់អាជ្ញាធរ។
backtrans: The war shouts for justice - much in the authorities' accusation.

sentence: The regime's decision adumbrates the underlying agenda.
Khmer: ការសម្រេចចិត្តរបស់របបនេះ adumbrates របៀបវារៈមូលដ្ឋាន។
backtrans: The decision of the regime adumbrates the basic agenda.

sentence: The community was anxious over the passing of the much needed reforms.
Khmer: សហគមន៍មានការអន្ទះសាធំជុំវិញការឆ្លងកាត់កំណែទម្រង់ដែលត្រូវការ។
backtrans: The community is anxious around the passing of reform.

sentence: The think tank  published a paper outlining their apology of capital punishment.
Khmer: ក្រុមអ្នកគិតបានចេញផ្សាយក្រដាសមួយដែលបង្ហាញពីការសុំទោសរបស់ពួកគេចំពោះការដាក់ទណ្ឌកម្មមូលធន។
backtrans: Thinkers released a paper showing their apology for the capital punishment.

sentence: Aught was left of the petition's validity
Khmer: Aught នៅសល់នៃសុពលភាពរបស់ញត្តិ
backtrans: Aught rest of the validity of the petition

sentence: The President exhorted his ministers to buckle up as key opposition support for his economic plan was about to buckle.
Khmer: លោកប្រធានាធិបតីបានដាស់តឿនរដ្ឋមន្ត្រីការរួមរបស់ខ្លួនឱ្យមានការគាំទ្រយ៉ាងខ្លាំងចំពោះផែនការសេដ្ឋកិច្ចរបស់លោកគឺចង់តម្កល់។
backtrans: The president admonished its own ministers to have a strong support for his economic plans, wanting to be made up.

sentence: The voters were chuffed to see the bill passed.
Khmer: អ្នកបោះឆ្នោតត្រូវបានគេចុកឡើងនៅពេលឃើញវិក័យប័ត្របានឆ្លងកាត់។
backtrans: Voters are fed up to see the bill crossed.

sentence: The lawyer's discursive narration swayed the jury.
Khmer: ការនិទានកថាដ៏ក្លករបស់មេធាវីបានធ្វើឱ្យមានគណៈវិនិច្ឆ័យ។
backtrans: The clinical narrative of the lawyer made a jury.

Khmer: លោកតុលាការបានចូលរួមបំផ្លាញអំពើហឹង្សានេះ!
backtrans: The court has contributed to the violence!

sentence: The EU block opposed an eventual imposition of anti-dumping measures.
Khmer: បណ្តុរសហភាពអឺរ៉ុបបានប្រឆាំងនឹងការដាក់វិធានការប្រឆាំងនឹងការបោះចោល។
backtrans: The European Union mouse opposes the restrictions against disposal.

sentence: A fulsome eulogy was delivered by the sly counsel.
Khmer: ពាក្យសរសើរដាច់ ៗ ត្រូវបានចែកចាយដោយដំបូន្មានរបស់ SLY ។
backtrans: Defacted words are distributed by Sly's advice.

sentence: The gig-economy agency decided to garnish the refunds!
Khmer: ទីភ្នាក់ងារសេដ្ឋកិច្ចជីជីបានសម្រេចចិត្តធ្វើឱ្យមានការសងប្រាក់វិញ!
backtrans: GIG economic agency decided to make refund!

sentence: Members of the anti-theocratic revolutionary movement overthrew the peers in power!
Khmer: សមាជិកនៃចលនាប្រឆាំងបដិរូបត្ថម្ភបានទម្លាក់មិត្តភក្តិនេះ!
backtrans: Members of anti-feed movements have dropped this friend!

sentence: The traitors disappointingly decided to fight with the colonialists.
Khmer: ជនក្បត់ដែលខកខានមិនបានធ្វើឱ្យមានការប្រយុទ្ធប្រឆាំងនឹងពួកអាណានិគមនិយម។
backtrans: The traitors failed to have a fight against colonism.
